snippet.title: CommanderTux walkthrough
snippet.description:
Game I made in 2005 using SDL 1.2 and C++. I now ported it to SDL 2.0, so it should run fine on more modern hardware. The video shows a walkthrough of all levels.

EXE file for Windows can be downloaded here:
https://github.com/0x17/SDL2CommanderTux/releases/tag/1.0

Source code can be found here: https://github.com/0x17/SDL2CommanderTux
